(
    '948fc375-bf15-392e-9ff1-d9d027466986',
    '7714c314-8f64-391d-b7e9-e01fcc5ec185',
    'Both step 1 and 2, think about stepping straight forward, forward, do not curve into Man, do not turn too early (don''t turn late either). Legs are ahead of body. Big step. Stay connected with Man. Work the R side a lot to stay with Man.',
    1
),
(
    '9c883c35-9fbd-319c-af4c-9a79ec7bc7a9',
    '7714c314-8f64-391d-b7e9-e01fcc5ec185',
    'Shaping: starting from PP (L hip up). on count 1, R hip begins to pick up.',
